---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - AIToolGuide">
  <div class="legal-page">
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="header">
      <div class="container">
        <nav class="nav">
          <a href="/" class="logo">
            <span class="logo-icon">💰</span>
            <span class="logo-text">AIToolGuide</span>
          </a>
          <div class="nav-actions">
            <a href="/" class="back-link">← Back to Home</a>
          </div>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Content -->
    <section class="legal-content">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: March 26, 2026</p>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
          <p>AIToolGuide ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
          <h3>2.1 Personal Information</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Email address (when you register)</li>
            <li>Password (encrypted)</li>
            <li>Language preference</li>
            <li>User-generated content (success stories, comments)</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3>2.2 Usage Data</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>IP address</li>
            <li>Browser type and version</li>
            <li>Pages visited</li>
            <li>Time spent on pages</li>
            <li>Referring website</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Provide and maintain our services</li>
            <li>Personalize your experience</li>
            <li>Send newsletters and updates (with consent)</li>
            <li>Improve our website and tools</li>
            <li>Respond to your inquiries</li>
            <li>Prevent fraud and abuse</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>4. Data Storage</h2>
          <p>We use localStorage to store your preferences and login session. This data is stored locally in your browser and is not transmitted to our servers unless you explicitly submit information.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>5. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p>We may use third-party services for:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Analytics (Google Analytics)</li>
            <li>Authentication (Clerk)</li>
            <li>Hosting (Vercel)</li>
          </ul>
          <p>These services have their own privacy policies.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>You have the right to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Access your personal data</li>
            <li>Correct inaccurate data</li>
            <li>Delete your account and data</li>
            <li>Opt-out of marketing communications</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at:</p>
          <p><a href="mailto:privacy@ai2424.com">privacy@ai2424.com</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <style>
    .legal-page {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 50%, #0f172a 100%);
    }

    .header {
      padding: 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: white;
    }

    .logo-icon { font-size: 1.8rem; }
    .logo-text {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }

    .nav-actions {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .back-link {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    .back-link:hover {
      color: white;
    }

    .legal-content {
      padding: 60px 20px;
      color: white;
    }

    .legal-content h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .last-updated {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .legal-section {
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .legal-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      color: #667eea;
    }

    .legal-section h3 {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 20px 0 12px;
    }

    .legal-section p {
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .legal-section ul {
      margin-left: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .legal-section li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .legal-section a {
      color: #667eea;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .legal-section a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .legal-content h1 {
        font-size: 1.75rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
